=Description=

"How do you build coalitions of the willing? A fast-moving, networked economy rewards successful interaction and iteration. We were therefore delighted to host '[[Co-Creation]] Rules' which sought to '''uncover the skills required for extreme collaboration that is fast becoming essential to innovation'''.

Johnnie Moore and James Cherkoff acted as ringmasters for the evening. They have worked in the UK, Europe and the USA in both the public and private sector and shared their experience of helping organisations understand how to harness the power of co-creation. They shared a series of examples using a highly interactive format."
(http://www.nesta.org.uk/)


